STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Tykel Dupree ROBINSON, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1416 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

The appellant appeals his conviction and sentence of robbery in the first degree. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED. REMANDED.
